NOTES: 
  Nothing much has changed but a plastic bunch of bananas is on its way and for the Roomba idea, the bananas can make a protective
  shroud which can be designed to look like a thrown for a glove monkey to sit on. It can have a servo in its neck to make its
  head look side to side and using the 360 degree camera a "A Day in the Life of a Monkey King" can be made with the tiny planet
